aption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETiffany%20Chan%20and%20her%20partner%20Anders%20brought%20home%20Siu%20Tam%2C%20a%20golden%20retriever%2C%20in%20November%202019.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20the%20couple%20paid%20%2440%2C000%20to%20take%20their%20pet%20on%20a%2053-day%20vacation%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChan%20says%20it%20was%20worth%20every%20penny%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they've%20already%20returned%20for%20a%20second%20trip.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Tiffany%20Chan%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20dog%20owner%20based%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%20This%20essay%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20verified%20Chan's%20receipts.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20boyfriend%20Anders%20and%20I%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhong-kong-millennial-housing-prices-income-debt-dreams-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebased%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20last%20year%20we%20spent%20around%20%2440%2C000%20to%20take%20our%20dog%20on%20vacation%20in%20Japan.%20It%20was%20magical%20to%20watch%20Siu%20Tim%20experience%20his%20first%20snowfall%20and%20frolic%20through%20Japan's%20breathtaking%20landscapes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnders%20and%20I%20are%20both%2032.%20He%20works%20in%20the%20IT%20industry%2C%20and%20I%20run%20a%20pet%20bakery.%20We%20brought%20Siu%20Tim%20home%20when%20he%20was%20three%20months%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20initially%20planned%20for%20a%20smaller%20breed%2C%20like%20a%20pug%20or%20a%20French%20Bulldog%2C%20the%20moment%20we%20laid%20eyes%20on%20Siu%20Tim%20at%20a%20pet%20shop%20in%20Mong%20Kok%2C%20we%20knew%20he%20was%20meant%20for%20us.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20around%20four%20or%20five%20months%20old%2C%20we%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20travel%20with%20Siu%20Tim%2C%20but%20COVID-19%20paused%20our%20plans%20for%20three%20years.%20When%20he%20turned%20three%20and%20restrictions%20eased%2C%20we%20embarked%20on%20our%20first%20trip%20together%2C%20deciding%20to%20seize%20the%20opportunity%20while%20he%20was%20still%20full%20of%20energy%20and%20playfulness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EExtra%20paperwork%2C%20planning%20time%2C%20and%20fees%20were%20required%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Checking%20in%20Golden%20Retriever%20at%20the%20airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d6b86cf533b039a885da14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESiu%20Tim%20at%20check-in%20before%20flight%20to%20Japan.%3Cp%3ETiffany%20Chan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-japan-healthcare-travel-expenses-comparison-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eset%20our%20sights%20on%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20our%20first%20international%20adventure.%20Known%20for%20its%20pet-friendly%20atmosphere%20and%20diverse%20seasons%2C%20it%20was%20the%20perfect%20fit%20for%20Siu%20Tim.%20With%20a%20flight%20just%20over%20four%20hours%2C%20Japan%20seemed%20a%20more%20manageable%20choice%20compared%20to%20Europe's%20lengthy%20journey%20from%20Hong%20Kong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20September%2C%20we%20enlisted%20the%20help%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhong-kong-pet-exodus-chartering-private-jets-covid-measures-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epet%20relocation%20agency%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20assist%20us%20with%20the%20travel%20requirements%20for%20Japan.%20Given%20the%20necessary%20180-day%20lead%20time%20for%20documentation%2C%20we%20kicked%20off%20the%20process%20promptly.%20By%20mid-March%202023%2C%20we%20were%20ready%20to%20embark%20on%20our%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%241%2C720%20fee%20from%20the%20relocation%20agency%20included%20the%20shipping%20crate%2C%20an%20import%20permit%2C%20a%20rabies%20vaccination%2C%20blood%20tests%2C%20and%20various%20handling%20fees.%20The%20airline%20charged%20an%20additional%20overseas%20courier%20service%20fee%20of%20%241%2C615.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20our%20flight%2C%20we%20arrived%20at%20the%20airport%202.5%20hours%20ahead%20to%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20boarding%20process%20for%20Siu%20Tim.%20After%20sorting%20out%20the%20paperwork%2C%20we%20gave%20him%20one%20last%20bathroom%20break%20before%20settling%20him%20into%20his%20crate%20at%20the%20designated%20drop-off.%20Though%20he%20entered%20without%20resistance%2C%20his%20cries%20hinted%20at%20his%20awareness%20of%20our%20impending%20departure.%20Witnessing%20his%20distress%2C%20even%20briefly%2C%20brought%20tears%20to%20my%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20sadness%20wore%20off%20quickly%2C%20as%20his%20excitement%20was%20palpable%20when%20we%20fetched%20him%20from%20the%20animal%20holding%20area%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnine-hours-capsule-pod-hotel-tokyo-narita-airport-review-photos-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENarita%20Airport%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20first%20task%20was%20whisking%20him%20off%20to%20the%20quarantine%20facility%20for%20chip%20verification%20and%20completing%20the%20essential%20paperwork%20for%20entry%20into%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20visited%2026%20prefectures%20in%20Japan%20over%20the%20course%20of%2053%20days.%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224672%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Golden%20retriever%20dressed%20up%20in%20a%20kimono%20in%20Japan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d6b77aa610a9069d5b1be4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESiu%20Tim%20dressed%20up%20in%20Kyoto%20for%20a%20kimono%20photo%20shoot.%3Cp%3ETiffany%20Chan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20itinerary%20spanned%20iconic%20tourist%20attractions%20like%20Asakusa%20Temple%20in%20To