sacrifice%20entirely%20worthwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20we%20revisited%20Japan%20with%20Siu%20Tim.%20We%20thought%20Japan%20again%20would%20make%20the%20most%20sense%20for%20its%20smooth%20process%2C%20having%20already%20completed%20all%20necessary%20paperwork%20and%20tests.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20second%20trip%2C%20we%20planned%20a%20less%20packed%20itinerary%20to%20avoid%20travel%20fatigue.%20We%20opted%20for%20longer%20stays%20at%20each%20location%2C%20minimizing%20hotel%20changes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20next%20vacation%2C%20we've%20decided%20to%20start%20saving%20up%20to%20take%20Siu%20Tim%20on%20a%20European%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacation-japan-dog-pet-holiday-expensive-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708578784000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d6b306a3bd891424f91d3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacation-japan-dog-pet-holiday-expensive-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20the%20paperwork%20and%20steep%20cost%2C%20Tiffany%20Chan%20has%20already%20returned%20for%20a%20second%20trip%20to%20Japan%20with%20her%20dog.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Faye%20Bradley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacation-japan-dog-pet-holiday-expensive-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vicky-%20Katrina%20spotted%20in%20London%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708578559000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107900775%2Cimgsize-25382.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkatrina-kaif-and-vicky-kaushal-spotted-on-brunch-date-in-london-fans-ask-to-meet-anushka-sharma-or-for-medical-treat