%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-circumvent-sanctions-china-turkey-banks-putin-price-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20has%20to%20pay%20intermediary%20fees%20to%20banks%20in%20China%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20Central%20Asia%20even%20if%20they%20are%20willing%20to%20transact%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Western%20sanctions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-circumvent-sanctions-china-turkey-banks-putin-price-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gujarat%20Home%20Minister%20Brags%20About%20Demolishing%20108%20Mazars%2C%20Says%20State's%20Bulldozer%20Is%20Everywhere%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EGujarat%20home%20minister%20Harsh%20Sanghavi%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20state%20government%20has%20demolished%20108%20mazars%20in%20its%20crackdown%20on%20%E2%80%98illegal%20encroachment%E2%80%99.%20He%20also%20claimed%20in%20the%20assembly%20that%20chief%20minister%20Bhupendra%20Patel%20was%20sending%20a%20bulldozer%20across%20the%20state%20to%20deal%20with%20such%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20the%20point%20mentioned%20by%20Amitbhai%20%5Bthe%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Ellisbridge%5D%E2%80%A6%20He%20said%20that%20a%20derasar%20was%20removed%20in%20Jamalpur.%20Now%2C%20Dada%E2%80%99s%20%5BBhupendra%20Patel%E2%80%99s%5D%20bulldozer%20is%20moving%20around%20in%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20the%20state%20so%20that%20no%20temple%20or%20devsthan%20can%20be%20removed%20while%20hatching%20a%20conspiracy.%20Nobody%20knows%20where%20will%20it%20%5Bthe%20bulldozer%5D%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2F108-mazars-demolished-cms-bulldozer-moving-around-gujarat-home-minister-101708567317031.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Csudden%E2%80%9D%20appearances%20of%20mazars%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cconspiracy%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20claimed%20in%20his%20speech%20meant%20to%20seek%20approval%20of%20the%20budgetary%20allocation%20for%20his%20ministry.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Uparkot%2C%20it%20was%20not%20known%20where%20(and%20when)%20all%20mazars%20were%20built.%20How%20can%20it%20be%20built%20suddenly%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20all%2C%20108%20mazars%20have%20been%20demolished%20(in%20the%20state)%20and%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20properties%20have%20been%20opened%E2%80%A6%20The%20encroachment%20around%20Somnath%20has%20been%20removed.%20This%20bulldozer%20of%20Dada%20can%20enter%20a%2020-ft%20wide%20street%20and%20an%2080-m%20wide%20road%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanghavi%20also%20used%20this%20opportunity%20to%20criticise%20those%20arguing%20that%20late-night%20Navratri%20celebrations%20were%20causing%20a%20disturbance.%20%E2%80%9CNavratri%20was%20allowed%20(to%20be%20celebrated)%20the%20whole%20night%20so%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Gujarat%20could%20worship%20the%20goddess%20and%20play%20raas%20throughout%20the%20night.%20Considering%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20(Gujarat)%20high%20court%20and%20its%20fear%2C%20we%20definitely%20got%20the%20sound%20(of%20music)%20decreased%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20because%20Navratri%20could%20be%20allowed%20till%20late%20night%2C%20it%20brought%20Diwali%20to%20numerous%20households.%20To%20get%20a%20figure%20of%20that%20(how%20many%20households)%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20ask%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20vendors%20and%20those%20running%20small%20restaurants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CI%20made%20a%20statement%20(then)%20that%20if%20the%20people%20of%20my%20state%20cannot%20perform%20garba%20then%20would%20they%20do%20so%20in%20Pakistan%3F%20The%20very%20next%20day%20of%20this%20statement%2C%20people%20from%20a%20party%20(moved)%20a%20PIL%20in%20the%20HC.%20They%20have%20a%20problem%20if%20people%20of%20the%20state%20perform%20garba%20till%20late%20in%20the%20night.%20Can%E2%80%99t%20people%20perform%20garba%20till%20late%3F%20We%20had%20to%20face%20that%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fin-selective-demolition-muslim-structures-razed-but-temple-spared-in-gujarats-dwarka%5C%22%3Ehas%20reported%20in%20the%20past%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20Sanghavi%20and%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20eagerness%20to%20raze%20Muslim%20structures%20%E2%80%93%20while%20seemingly%20ignoring%20Hindu%20ones%20that%20violate%20the%20same%20encroachment%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708577264000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgujarat-home-minister-brags-about-demolishing-108-mazars-says-states-bulldozer-is-everywhere%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNow%2C%20Dada%E2%80%99s%20%5BBhupendra%20Patel's%5D%20bulldozer%20is%20moving%20around%20in%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20the%20state%20so%20that%20no%20temple%20or%20devsthan%20can%20be%20removed%20while%20hatching%20a%20conspiracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgujarat-home-minister-brags-about-demolishing-108-mazars-says-states-bulldozer-is-everywhere%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TBMAUJ%20mint%20Rs%201.75%20crore%20continuing%20its%20steady%20run%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708577209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107901317%2Cimgsize-53272.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fteri-baaton-mein-aisa