0between%2024%20and%2046.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELife%20of%20limited%20flexibility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20patients%20are%20across%20the%20world%2C%20I%20have%20to%20work%20unusual%20hours.%20I%20work%20three%20days%20a%20week%20from%204%20a.m.%20until%201%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20end%20my%20days%20at%205%20p.m.%2C%20and%20stay%20in%20one%20place%20for%20several%20days%2C%20which%20left%20very%20little%20room%20for%20exploring.%20Back%20then%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20set%20up%20hotspots%20or%20organize%20my%20day%20by%20working%20early%20mornings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20digital%20nomad%2C%20I%20always%20have%20something%20to%20worry%20about.%20I%20could%20never%20be%20one%20of%20those%20backpackers%20that%20say%20%26quot%3Bit%20doesn't%20matter%20if%20we%20are%20sleeping%20in%20a%20tent%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20if%20we%20don't%20find%20a%20hostel%26quot%3B%20because%20I%20always%20need%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girl%20sitting%20on%20a%20cliff%20near%20an%20island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d56a9ea610a9069d5ac765%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20a%20digital%20nomad%2C%20Villafuerte%20often%20has%20to%20book%20flights%20last%20minute%20and%20travel%20with%20heavy%20electronics.%3Cp%3ECarolina%20Villafuerte%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20travel%20with%20a%20laptop%20because%20a%20phone%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20store%20all%20my%20patients'%20archives.%20I%20also%20bring%20along%20two%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20plan%20all%20my%20trips%20and%20activities%20around%20my%20calls.%20My%20trips%20get%20expensive%20because%20I%20book%20flights%20last%20minute.%20Being%20from%20Ecuador%2C%20I%20need%20visas%20for%20most%20places%20and%20there%20is%20no%20guarantee%20of%20when%20those%20will%20arrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20all%20the%20time%20a