on%20in%20the%20next%20three%20months%20was%20unlikely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSE%20Sensex%20index%2C%20closely%20tracking%20the%20U.S.%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%2C%20climbed%20nearly%2019%25%20last%20year%20on%20expectations%20global%20central%20banks%20will%20cut%20interest%20rates%20in%202024%20and%20India's%20economic%20growth%20will%20outpace%20its%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaching%20the%2073%2C000%20mark%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20January%2C%20the%20benchmark%20index%20is%20up%20over%201%25%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20despite%20fading%20speculation%20about%20early%20rate%20cuts%20from%20the%20U.S.%20Federal%20Reserve%20triggering%20foreign%20portfolio%20outflows%20from%20many%20emerging%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOptimism%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20has%20also%20been%20driven%20by%20expectations%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20will%20retain%20power%20in%20the%20upcoming%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Feb.%2012-21%20Reuters%20poll%20of%2028%20equity%20analysts%20forecast%20the%20Sensex%20index%20would%20add%20another%204%25%20to%20reach%20a%20high%20of%2076%2C000%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20far%20above%20the%2070%2C000%20level%20expected%20in%20a%20November%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Tuesday's%20close%20of%2073%2C057%2C%20the%20BSE%20index%20is%20forecast%20to%20rise%207.5%25%20to%2078%2C550%20at%20the%20end%20of%202024.%20That%20would%20be%20around%20a%209%25%20gain%20for%20the%20entire%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20economy%20remains%20a%20'star%20performing'%20economy%20against%20other%20emerging%20markets.%20Moreover%2C%20we%20firmly%20believe%20it%20will%20likely%20continue%20its%20growth%20momentum%20in%202024%20and%20remain%20the%20land%20of%20stability%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20volatile%20global%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Neeraj%20Chadawar%2C%20head%20of%20quantitative%20equ