C%22Mickey%20Arthur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F42542-john-michael-arthur-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMickey%20Arthur%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Grant%20Bradburn%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F132-grant-bradburn-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGrant%20Bradburn%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20given%20team%20fitness%20lowest%20priority%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%20India.%20Pakistan%2C%20under%20then-skipper%20Babar%2C%20had%20failed%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20semifinal%20knockout%20round%2C%20losing%20five%20of%20the%20nine%20league%20games%20and%20finishing%20fifth.%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20recently%20did%20not%20renew%20Hafeez's%20contract%20following%20disastrous%20tours%20of%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand.%20Hafeez%20was%20made%20team%20director%20in%20late%202023%20after%20Pakistan's%20abysmal%20show%20in%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20he%20took%20charge%2C%20Pakistan%20were%20whitewashed%20in%20the%20three-Test%20series%20down%20under%2C%20while%20they%20lost%20the%20five-match%20T20I%20series%20against%20the%20Kiwis%204-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20took%20over%20as%20director%20(in%202023)%20and%20we%20reached%20Australia%2C%20I%20told%20the%20team%20trainer%20to%20give%20me%20a%20report%20on%20the%20players'%20fitness%20standards%20and%20prepare%20a%20new%20fitness%20regimen%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hafeez.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20told%20me%20that%20the%20former%20captain%20(Babar)%20and%20head%20coach%20(Arthur)%20had%20told%20him%20six%20months%20ago%20that%20fitness%20is%20not%20the%20priority%20at%20the%20moment%20and%20let%20the%20players%20play%20as%20they%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20Hafeez%20revealed%20on%20the%20ARY%20sports%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20shocking%20news%20for%20me%20when%20he%20(team%20trainer)%20told%20me%20that%20he%20was%20told%20to%20not%20check%20the%20players%20fitness%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Hafeez.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHafeez%20said%20that%20when%20he%20checked%20the%20body%20fat%20percentage%20and%20endurance%20levels%20of%20the%20players%2C%20it%20was%20way%20below%20the%20international%20cricket%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFitness%20in%20modern-day%20cricket%20is%20top%20priority%20for%20all%20teams.%26quot%3B%20Hafeez%20alleged%20that%20when%20tests%20were%20carried%20out%20on%20some%20players%20in%20Australia%2C%20they%20couldn't%20even%20finish%20a%20two-km%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20players'%20skin%20fold%20(body%20fat%20level)%20was%20one-and-a-half%20points%20above%20the%20normal%20limit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Test%20captain%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Azhar%20Ali%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1468-azhar-ali-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAzhar%20Ali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20experts%20on%20the%20TV%20show%2C%20recalled%20that%20when%20Pakistan%20had%20gone%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20England%20in%202017%2C%20fitness%20was%20given%20top%20priority%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20the%20coaching%20staff%20sent%20a%20player%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Umar%20Akmal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1043-umar-akmal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EUmar%20Akmal%3C%2Fa%3E)%20back%20because%20he%20had%20failed%20a%20fitness%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArthur%20was%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20team%20that%20won%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20beating%20India%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHafeez%20also%20said%20that%20it%20took%20him%20three%20months%20to%20convince%20Babar%20Azam%20to%20leave%20his%20opening%20slot%20and%20bat%20at%20number%203%20in%20T20%20cricket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%2