0the%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20rampant%20unemployment%20and%20underemployment%20a%20major%20reality%20of%20the%20youth%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20across%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Opposition%20hopes%20to%20corner%20the%20government%20on%20the%20issue%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708569002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20152728%2Fsignal-2024-02-20-152659_002.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Flakh-aspirants-jobs-exams-constable-recruitment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fake%20candidates%2C%20paper%20leak%20allegations%20and%20more%20%E2%80%93%20the%20examination%20was%20conducted%20amid%20allegations%20of%20irregularities%20and%20questions%20were%20being%20raised%20over%20its%20fairness%20by%20aspirants%20as%20well%20as%20opposition%20parties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Flakh-aspirants-jobs-exams-constable-recruitment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Whale%20song%20mystery%20solved%20by%20scientists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708568949000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FD80E%2Fproduction%2F_132701355_humpbackwhalebreaching_filatova.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68358414%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20deduce%20how%20whales%20sing%20under%20the%20sea%2C%20and%20why%20they%20can%20be%20drowned%20out%20by%20noisy%20ships.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A62%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68358414%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68358414.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscie