primary%20role%20in%20government%20initiatives%2C%20Aadhaar%20has%20gained%20prominence%20as%20vital%20identity%20proof%20across%20diverse%20sectors.%20This%20is%20attributed%20to%20the%20comprehensive%20information%20it%20encapsulates%2C%20including%20citizens'%20full%20names%2C%20permanent%20addresses%2C%20and%20dates%20of%20birth%2C%20all%20intricately%20linked%20to%20a%20distinctive%2012-digit%20number%20assigned%20by%20the%20Unique%20Identification%20Authority%20of%20India%20(UIDAI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAadhaar%20cards%20are%20available%20in%20two%20distinct%20categories%20to%20cater%20to%20different%20demographics.%20The%20first%20category%20is%20tailored%20for%20adults%2C%20encompassing%20the%20standard%20Aadhaar%20card.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20second%20category%20is%20specifically%20designed%20for%20children%20and%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20'Baal%20Aadhaar.'%20This%20specialized%20version%20allows%20parents%20the%20flexibility%20to%20apply%20for%20an%20Aadhaar%20card%20for%20their%20newborns%2C%20ensuring%20a%20seamless%20process%20for%20enrollment%20and%20documentation%20right%20from%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20a%20child's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuidai.gov.in%2Fen%2Fmedia-resources%2Fuidai-documents%2Fparliament-questions%2Flok-sabha%2F4146-baal-aadhaar-card.html%5C%22%3EUIDAI%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20'Baal%20Aadhaar'%2C%20printed%20in%20a%20blue%20coloured%20letter%20for%20communicating%20the%20Aadhaar%20number%20to%20children%20under%20five%20years%20old%2C%20has%20been%20introduced%20by%20UIDAI.%20The%20letter%20informs%20the%20Aadhaar%20holder%20(parents)%20to%20update%20the%20Aadhaar%20details%20with%20biometrics%20on%20attaining%20the%20age%20of%20five%20years%2C%20failing%20which%20Aadhaar%20will%20be%20deactivated%20and%20will%20not%20be%20valid.%20A%20blue-coloured%20letter%20has%20been%20introduced%20to%20visibly%20distinguish%20the%20letter%20for%20children%2C%20for%20ease%20of%20mass%20communication%20to%20people%20to%20get%20the%20biometrics%20of%20their%20children%20updated%20on%20attaining%20the%20age%20of%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Section%203(1)%20of%20the%20Aadhaar%20Act%2C%202016%2C%20every%20resident%20is%20entitled%20to%20obtain%20an%20Aadhaar%20number%2C%20including%20children%2C%20by%20submitting%20his%20demographic%20information%20and%20biometric%20information%20during%20the%20process%20of%20enrolment.%20For%20enrolment%20of%20children%20under%205%20years%20old%2C%20biometric%20information%20is%20not%20collected%2C%20only%20demographic%20and%20photograph%20information%20is%20collected.%20The%20Aadhaar%20number%20of%20the%20child%20is%20linked%20with%20either%20of%20the%20parent's%20Aadhaar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20biometric%20data%20on%20the%20child%20is%20required%20for%20'Baal%20Aadhaar'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20children%20under%205%20years%20old%2C%20no%20biometrics%20will%20be%20captured.%20Their%20UID%20will%20be%20processed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20demographic%20information%20and%20a%20facial%20photograph%20linked%20to%20the%20UID%20of%20their%20parents.%20These%20children%20will%20need%20to%20update%20their%20biometrics%20of%20ten%20fingers%2C%20an%20iris%2C%20and%20a%20facial%20photograph%2C%20when%20they%20turn%205%20and%2015.%20Intimation%20to%20this%20effect%20will%20be%20mentioned%20in%20the%20original%20Aadhaar%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20how%20to%20easily%20book%20an%20appointment%20for%20your%20child's%20Aadhaar%20card%20online%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Head%20to%20the%20official%20website%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisit%20the%20Unique%20Identification%20Authority%20of%20India%20(UIDAI)%20website%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuidai.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fuidai.gov.in%2F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Navigate%20to%20%26quot%3BMy%20Aadhaar%26quot%3B%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFind%20the%20%26quot%3BMy%20Aadhaar%26quot%3B%20section%20and%20click%20on%20%26quot%3BBook%20an%20Appointment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Choose%20%26quot%3BChild%20Aadhaar%26quot%3B%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESelect%20%26quot%3BNew%20Aadhaar%26quot%3B%20and%20enter%20your%20mobile%20number%20and%20the%20security%20code%20(captcha).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20%26quot%3BRelationship%20with%20Head%20of%20Family%2C%26quot%3B%20choose%20%26quot%3BChild%20(0-5%20years).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Fill%20in%20Your%20Child's%20Details%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarefully%20enter%20your%20child's%20information%2C%20including%20name%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20and%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnsure%20you%20have%20the%20required%20documents%3A%20your%20child's%20birth%20certificate%20and%20your%20own%20Aadhaar%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Book%20Your%20Appointment%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoose%20a%20convenient%20date%20and%20time%20at%20a%20nearby%20Aadhaar%20Seva%20Kendra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfirm%20your%20booking%2C%20and%20you're%20all%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20how%20to%20get%20your%20child's%20Aadhaar%20card%20(Blue%20Aadhaar)%20offline%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Find%20an%20Enrollment%20Center%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisit%20any%20Aadhaar%20Seva%20Kendra%20or%20Permanent%20Enrollment%20Center.%20You%20can%20locate%20one%20near%20you%20on%20the%20UIDAI%20website%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fuidai.gov.in%2F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Inform%20the%20officials%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETell%20them%20you%20want%20to%20enroll%20your%20child%20for%20a%20Blue%20Aadhaar%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Fill%20out%20the%20form%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarefully%20complete%20the%20Aadhaar%20enrollment%20form%20with%20your%20child's%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Gather%20the%20documents%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20sure%20you%20have%20the%20following%20documents%20readily%20available%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnYour%20Aadhaar%20card%3A%20As%20proof%20of%20parentage.%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20child's%20birth%20certificate%3A%20As%20proof%20of%20birth%20and%20identity.%3Cbr%3E%5CnYour%20address%20proof%3A%20Ration%20card%2C%20electricity%20bill%2C%20etc.%3Cbr%3E%5CnTwo%20passport-sized%20photos%20of%20your%20child%3A%20Optional%2C%20but%20helpful%20if%20the%20center's%20photo%20service%20is%20unavailable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Submit%20Your%20Application%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHand%20over%20the%20completed%20form%20and%20all%20the%20required%20documents%20to%20the%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708568040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Ftqhviek_aadhaar-card-650_625x300_11_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaal-aadhaar-card-blue-aadhaar-for-your-child-what-it-is-how-to-apply-and-more-5103976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parents%20have%20the%20option%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20Baal%20Aadhaar%20Card%2C%20commonly%20known%20as%20Blue%20Aadhaar%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20their%20newborns.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaal-aadhaar-card-blue-aadhaar-for-your-child-what-it-is-how-to-apply-and-more-5103976%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaal-aadhaar-card-blue-aadhaar-for-your-child-what-it-is-how-to-apply-and-more-5103976%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaal-aadhaar-card-blue-aadhaar-for-your-child-what-it-is-how-to-apply-and-more-5103976%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Cop%20Who%20Killed%20Indian%20Student%20Let%20Go%20Due%20To%20%26quot%3BLack%20Of%20Evidence%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Seattle%20police%20officer%20who%20struck%20and%20killed%20Indian%20student%20Jaahnavi%20Kandula%20while%20responding%20to%20an%20overdose%20call%2C%20will%20not%20face%20any%20criminal%20charges%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20%26quot%3Bsufficient%26quot%3B%20evidence%2C%20authorities%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20King%20County%20Prosecutor's%20Office%20said%20they%20will%20not%20move%20forward%20with%20criminal%20charges%20against%20Seattle%20Police%20Officer%20Kevin%20Dave%2C%20FOX13%20Seattle%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20released%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20King%20County%20Prosecuting%20Attorney%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BKandula's%20death%20is%20heartbreaking%20and%20impacted%20communities%20in%20King%20County%20and%20across%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%20Kandula%2C%2023%2C%20was%20struck%20by%20a%20police%20vehicle%20driven%20by%20Officer%20Dave%20when%20she%20was%20crossing%20a%20street%20in%20Seattle%20on%20January%2023.%20He%20was%20driving%2074%20mph%20(more%20than%20119%20kmh)%20on%20the%20way%20to%20a%20report%20of%20a%20drug%20overdose%20call.%20Kandula%20was%20thrown%20100%20feet%20when%20she%20was%20struck%20by%20the%20speeding%20police%20patrol%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20bodycam%20footage%20released%20by%20the%20Seattle%20Police%20Department%2C%20Officer%20Daniel%20Auderer%20laughed%20about%20the%20deadly%20crash%20and%20dismissed%20any%20implication%20Dave%20might%20be%20at%20fault%20or%20that%20a%20criminal%20investigation%20was%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKing%20County%20Prosecuting%20Attorney%20Leesa%20Manion%20said%20that%20she%20believes%20they%20lack%20the%20evidence%20to%20prove%20a%20criminal%20case%20beyond%20a%20reasonable%20doubt%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20King%20County%20Prosecuting%20Attorney's%20Office%20to%20review%20all%20available%20evidence%20relating%20to%20the%20case%20involving%20Seattle%20Police%20Officer%20Kevin%20Dave%20and%20the%20January%202023%20collision%20death%20of%20Jaahnavi%20Kandula.%20After%20staffing%20this%20case%20with%20senior%20deputy%20prosecuting%20attorneys%20and%20office%20leadership%2C%20I%20have%20determined%20that%20we%20lack%20sufficient%20evidence%20under%20Washington%20State%20law%20to%20prove%20a%20criminal%20case%20beyond%20a%20reasonable%20doubt.%26quot%3B%20The%20statement%20also%20said%20that%20the%20prosecutor's%20office%20also%20finds%20the%20comments%20made%20by%20Seattle%20Police%20Officer%20Daniel%20Auderer%2C%20recorded%20on%20his%20body-worn%20video%2C%20%26quot%3Bappalling%20and%20deeply%20troubling.%26quot%3B%20Auderer%2C%20who%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20January%20collision%2C%20was%20captured%20in%20the%20video%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20she%20is%20dead%26quot%3B%20and%20laughing%20while%20on%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%2026%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20Auderer%20said%20in%20the%20video.%20%26quot%3BShe%20had%20limited%20value.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BOfficer%20Auderer's%20comments%20were%20also%20unprofessional%20and%20undermined%20the%20public's%20trust%20in%20the%20Seattle%20Police%20Department%20and%20law%20enforcement%20in%20general%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Manion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20egregious%20as%20Officer%20Auderer's%20comments%20are%2C%20they%20do%20not%20change%20the%20PAO's%20legal%20analysis%20into%20the%20conduct%20of%20Officer%20Dave.%20It%20is%20the%20Office%20of%20Police%20Accountability%20that%20bears%20the%20responsibility%20of%20disciplinary%20investigation%20and%20proceedings%20relating%20to%20Officer%20Auderer's%20comment%2C%20not%20the%20PAO.%26quot%3B%20Auderer%20was%20pulled%20from%20patrol%20in%20September%202023%20and%20reassigned%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bnon-operational%20position.%26quot%3B%20Auderer%20could%20still%20be%20fired%20after%20the%20fallout%20of%20his%20insensitive%20comments%20captured%20on%20bodycam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuderer's%20chain%20of%20command%20and%20the%20Office%20of%20Police%20Accountability%20(OPA)%20found%20he%20acted%20unprofessionally.%20For%20that%2C%20he%20faces%20the%20highest%20disciplinary%20range%20of%20nearly%20two%20weeks%20suspension%20up%20to%20termination%2C%20according%20to%20a%20disciplinary%20action%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20a%20final%20disciplinary%20decision%2C%20Auderer%20will%20have%20the%20chance%20to%20meet%20with%20Police%20Chief%20Adrian%20Diaz%20to%20disagree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20disciplinary%20hearing%20is%20scheduled%20for%20March%204%2C%20K5%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeattle%20local%20media%20reported%20that%20speed%20was%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20collision%2C%20as%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20Dave%20was%20travelling%20did%20%26quot%3Bnot%20allow%20(Kandula)%20or%20him%20sufficient%20time%20to%20detect%2C%20address%20and%20avoid%20a%20hazard%20that%20presented%20itself.%26quot%3B%20Dave%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bpriority%20one%26quot%3B%20call%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20Seattle%20Fire%20Department%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Seattle%20Police%20Department.%20According%20to%20the%20police%20report%2C%20the%20officer%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20report%20of%20a%20drug%20overdose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20did%20not%20have%20his%20siren%20activated%20continuously.%20Instead%2C%20the%20officer%20%26quot%3Bchirped%26quot%3B%20his%20siren%20at%20the%20intersection.%20He%20did%20have%20his%20emergency%20lights%20on%2C%20according%20to%20a%20previous%20statement%20from%20the%20police%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20memo%20to%20Seattle%20police%2C%20prosecutors%20wrote%20there%20was%20not%20enough%20evidence%20to%20prove%20Dave%20showed%20%26quot%3Bconscious%20disregard%20for%20others%20safety.%26quot%3B%20A%20drug%20recognition%20expert%20responded%20to%20the%20scene%20and%20found%20no%20impairment%20in%20the%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKandula%20was%20a%20graduate%20student%20at%20Northeastern%20University%20at%20the%20Seattle%20campus.%20The%20university%20said%20in%20January%202023%20that%20they%20would%20award%20her%20degree%20posthumously%20and%20present%20it%20to%20her%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20