up%20of%20shareholders%2C%20including%20tech%20investor%20giant%20Prosus%2C%20requested%20an%20extraordinary%20general%20meeting%20(EGM)%20set%20for%20February%2023%20to%20oust%20Raveendran%20and%20appoint%20a%20new%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Byju's%20said%20the%20karnataka%20High%20Court%20had%20ordered%20that%20any%20decisions%20taken%20by%20shareholders%20at%20the%20EGM%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Binvalid%26quot%3B%20until%20the%20next%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20said%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20EGM%20were%20%26quot%3Bmerely%20a%20smokescreen%20designed%20to%20disrupt%20the%20management%2C%20control%2C%20and%20functioning%20of%20the%20company%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFP%20has%20reviewed%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20interim%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestor%20sources%20told%20AFP%20that%20the%20court%20order%20did%20not%20prohibit%20the%20shareholder%20meeting%20from%20taking%20place%20or%20declare%20it%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20added%20that%20the%20EGM%20would%20go%20ahead%20and%20investors%20would%20still%20push%20to%20remove%20Raveendran%20as%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20has%20alleged%20that%20investors%2C%20including%20US%20growth%20equity%20firm%20General%20Atlantic%20and%20the%20Chan%20Zuckerberg%20Initiative%2C%20a%20philanthropic%20venture%20founded%20by%20Facebook%20boss%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20his%20wife%20Priscilla%20Chan%2C%20had%20violated%20their%20shareholders'%20agreement%20by%20calling%20the%20EGM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20of%20Prosus%20and%20the%20Chan%20Zuckerberg%20Initiative%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20Byju's%20board%20last%20year.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708565520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fd5dgeneg_byju-raveendran-divya-goku