0and%20geopolitical%20uncertainty%E2%80%94and%20we%20need%20to%20make%20purposeful%20changes%20now%20to%20ensure%20our%20promising%20future.%20We%20must%20strategically%20prioritize%20our%20growth%20areas%20of%20the%20business%2C%20including%20the%20launch%20of%20Peregrine%20and%20R2%20as%20well%20as%20investing%20in%20our%20go-to-market%20capabilities.%20We've%20recently%20implemented%20several%20organizational%20and%20leadership%20changes%2C%20but%20we%20need%20to%20do%20more%20to%20achieve%20our%20strategic%20priorities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETomorrow%2C%20February%2022%2C%20employees%20who%20are%20impacted%20will%20receive%20a%20calendar%20invite%20between%207%3A30%20and%208%20a.m.%20PT%20for%20a%201%3A1%20meeting%20with%20their%20manager%20later%20that%20same%20morning.%20We%20know%20the%20timing%20here%20is%20difficult%20%E2%80%93%20waiting%20between%20now%20and%20tomorrow%20to%20understand%20whether%20you're%20impacted%20is%20far%20from%20ideal%2C%20but%20we%20want%20to%20ensure%20a%20considerate%20notification%20process%20that%20accommodates%20all%20time%20zones.%20We%20will%20be%20doing%20everything%20we%20can%20to%20support%20our%20impacted%20colleagues%20through%20the%20separation%20process%2C%20including%20severance%2C%20eligibility%20for%20Rivian-paid%20COBRA%20benefits%20coverage%20and%20access%20to%20job%20placement%20services.%20Also%2C%20anyone%20impacted%20tomorrow%20will%20still%20be%20eligible%20for%20our%20FY'23%20bonus.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20recognize%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20isn't%20easy.%20I'm%20thankful%20for%20everyone's%20contributions%2C%20and%20for%20those%20who%20leave%20us%2C%20I%20want%20to%20thank%20you%20deeply%20for%20everything%20you've%20done%20for%20Rivian%2C%20and%20for%20what%20you've%20done%20to%20advance%20our%20mission.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERJ%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22htt