(upon%20her%20release%20in%202004%2C%20she%20was%20deported%20to%20Colombia%2C%20where%20she%20died%20of%20a%20gunshot%20wound%20in%202012).%20He%20briefly%20followed%20in%20his%20family's%20footsteps%20and%20dabbled%20in%20the%20drug%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Blanco%20is%20determined%20to%20make%20it%20by%20going%20legit%3A%20he's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymotherthegodmother.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewritten%20a%20book%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20says%20he's%20developing%20TV%20shows%20and%20movies.%20He's%20eager%20to%20prove%20that%20there%20is%20a%20future%20for%20the%20Blanco%20name%20beyond%20its%20notorious%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20from%20a%20drug%20trafficking%20family%2C%20and%20you're%20fucking%20Miami%20monarchy%2C%20Miami%20royalty%2C%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20for%20you%20to%20understand%20that%20that%20life%20has%20gone%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Blanco%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20evolve%20as%20a%20man.%20And%20the%20only%20way%20I%20could%20evolve%20was%20legalizing%20my%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20spoke%20over%20the%20phone%20with%20Corben%20and%20Blanco%20about%20why%20they%20teamed%20up%20for%20a%20podcast%2C%20the%20actor%20Blanco%20believes%20did%20the%20best%20portrayal%20of%20his%20mother%2C%20and%20how%20Corben%20got%20close%20to%20becoming%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20cocaine%20godmother's%20wrath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Billy%20Corben%20and%20Michael%20Corleone%20Blanco%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20microphones%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d53156a610a9069d5ac3a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20Billy%20Corben%20and%20Michael%20Corleone%20Blanco.%3Cp%3Erakontur%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20podcast%20makes%20it%20sound%20like%20you%20two%20have%20known%20each%20other%20for%20years.%20Billy%2C%20when%20was%20your%20first%20interaction%20with%20Michael%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20goes%20way%20back.%20It%20was%20probably%20between%20the%20release%20of%20%26quot%3BCocaine%20Cowboys%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCocaine%20Cowboys%202.%26quot%3B%20Michael%2C%20does%20that%20sound%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yeah.%20I%20would%20say%202006%20or%202007.%20I%20remember%20like%20it%20was%20yesterday%2C%20walking%20to%20The%20Colony%20Theatre%20for%20the%20second%20movie.%20Still%20being%20part%20of%20that%20underground%20world%20back%20then%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20statement.%20So%2C%20I%20showed%20up%20with%2020-30%20goons.%20I%20let%20people%20know%20South%20Beach%20was%20my%20stomping%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMichael%2C%20you%20speak%20on%20the%20podcast%20about%20the%20animosity%20you%20had%20toward%20Billy%20and%20his%20filmmaking%20partners%20at%20that%20time.%20When%20did%20you%20figure%20out%20that%20you%20could%20also%20make%20money%20off%20your%20family%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Not%20that%20long%20after%20that.%20One%20thing%20my%20mother%20taught%20me%20was%20how%20to%20pivot.%20From%20the%20moment%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20one%20of%20their%20movie's%20investors%20for%20the%20first%20movie%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20had%20to%20put%20some%20pep%20in%20my%20step%20and%20get%20on%20their%20level.%20I%20was%20a%20rookie%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20will%20say%20the%20smartest%20thing%20I%20ever%20did%20was%20not%20to%20listen%20to%20my%20lawyer%20or%20my%20mother%20and%20put%20a%20cease%20and%20desist%20on%20the%20first%20%26quot%3BCocaine%20Cowboys%26quot%3B%20movie.%20I%20knew%20that%20one%20day%2C%20the%20Griselda%20Blanco%20story%20and%20the%20Blanco%20family%20story%20would%20have%20to%20be%20told%2C%20and%20with%20them%20already%20telling%20some%20of%20the%20story%2C%20it%20was%20going%20to%20help%20me%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20when%20Billy%20put%20together%20the%20play%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcocaine-cowboys-being-made-into-a-play-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConfessions%20of%20a%20Cocaine%20Cowboy%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%202019%2C%20which%20also%20played%20at%20The%20Colony%2C%20I%20didn't%20see%20Billy%2C%20Alfred%2C%20and%20Dave%20as%20my%20archnemesis%20anymore.%20I%20remember%20having%20a%20drink%20with%20Billy%20back%20then%2C%20and%20I%20told%20him%20thank%20you.%20Because%20if%20it%20wasn't%20for%20that%20wave%20you%20created%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20here%20right%20now.%20Because%20now%20I%20make%20the%20big%20bucks.%20It's%20a%20full-circle%20moment%2C%20being%20on%20this%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAnd%20as%20much%20as%20Michael%20and%20his%20mother%20felt%20that%20something%20had%20been%20taken%20from%20them%2C%20remember%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ocala.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2F2006%2F10%2F28%2Ffilm-on-drug-trade-a-bootleg-hit%2F31173480007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCocaine%20Cowboys%26quot%3B%20blew%20up%20because%20of%20the%20bootleg%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20were%20sold%20in%20flea%20markets%2C%20barbershops%2C%20strip%20club%20bathrooms.%20Bootlegs%20of%20our%20movie%20was%20how%20it%20blew%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20would%20autograph%20their%20movie.%20It%20blew%20my%20mind.%20I%20had%20a%20tattoo%20parlor%2C%20and%20people%20would%20come%20in%20with%20the%20bootleg%20and%20ask%20if%20I%20could%20autograph%20it.%20Let%20me%20put%20it%20to%20you%20more%20plainly%3A%20I%20remember%20being%20in%20federal%20detention%2C%20and%20someone%20snuck%20in%20a%20DVD%2C%20and%20with%20his%20back%20to%20the%20security%20camera%2C%20someone%20would%20come%20up%20to%20me%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Blanco%2C%20can%20you%20sign%20this%20for%20my%20wife%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBilly%2C%20how%20close%20were%20you%20to%20not%20just%20doing%20a%20%26quot%3BCocaine%20Cowboys%26quot%3B%20documentary%20with%20the%20cooperation%20of%20Michael%2C%20but%20also%20getting%20Griselda%20on%20camera%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Michael%20can%20answer%20that%20better%20than%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20were%20one%20meeting%20away%20and%20around%20six%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%5B%3Cem%3ELaughs%3C%2Fem%3E.%5D%20Yeah.%20That%20sounds%20about%20accurate%20to%20me.%20As%20%26quot%3BCocaine%20Cowboys%26quot%3B%20turned%20into%20a%20franchise%20of%20documentaries%2C%20there%20was%20definitely%20a%20desire%20to%20have%20the%20story%20of%20%26quot%3BLa%20Madrina%26quot%3B%20told%20by%20La%20Madrina.%20The%20conversations%20continued%20but%20unfortunately%20did%20not%20consummate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20were%20almost%20there.%20Prior%20to%202012%2C%20my%20mother%20and%20I%20had%20the%20conversation.%20Money%20talks%20and%20bullshit%20runs%20the%20marathon.%20So%20when%20we%20were%20able%20to%20close%20not%20one%20but%20two%20motion%20picture%20deals%20based%20on%20her%20life%20rights%20and%20my%20life%20rights%2C%20by%20that%20time%2C%20my%20mother%20understood%20that%20we%20had%20something%20that%20the%20masses%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20gave%20me%20the%20power%20of%20attorney%2C%20and%20that's%20when%20I%20started%20negotiations%20with%20Billy.%20And%20like%20I%20said%2C%20I%20think%20we%20were%20one%20meeting%2C%20and%20probably%20six%20figures%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sofia%20Vergara%20as%20Griselda%20Blanco%20in%20%26quot%3BGriselda.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b67de3ac2de4f17ee52995%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESofia%20Vergara%20as%20Griselda%20Blanco%20in%20%26quot%3BGriselda.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Morris%2FNetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBilly%2C%20Michael%20says%20in%20the%20podcast%20that%20you%20%26quot%3Balmost%20got%20the%20knock%20on%20the%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20Griselda's%20thought%20of%20putting%20a%20hit%20on%20you.%20Back%20when%20you%20made%20the%20%26quot%3BCocaine%20Cowboys%26quot%3B%20movies%2C%20did%20you%20fear%20for%20your%20life%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20were%20pretty%20young%20and%20naive%20back%20then%2C%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20call%20it%20a%20fear%2C%20but%20I%20would%20very%20much%20call%20it%20a%20concern.%20We%20talked%20about%20it.%20We%20would%20hear%20from%20people%20whose%20parents%20were%20murdered%20during%20that%20time%20period%20in%20Miami.%20Some%20were%20depicted%20in%20the%20documentaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20was%20an%20offense%20that%20these%20stories%20were%20being%20let%20out%20of%20the%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20assume%20you%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20gives%20these%20people%20the%20right%20to%20tell%20the%20public%20what%20I%20know%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yeah.%20And%20now%20it's%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20the%20hell%20are%20you%20to%20tell%20me%20and%20Billy%20Corben%20about%20what%20went%20down%3F%20We're%20the%20fucking%20experts!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBilly%2C%20is%20that%20what%20led%20to%20making%20%26quot%3BThe%20Real%20Griselda%26quot%3B%20podcast%3F%20Basically%20fact-checking%20the%20Netflix%20%26quot%3BGriselda%26quot%3B%20show%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20was%20one%20of%20those%20things%20where%20it%20develops%20really%20slowly%2C%20and%20then%20something%20happens%20that%20just%20accelerates%20that%20plan.%20And%20what's%20amazing%20about%20this%20is%20we%20basically%20came%20up%20with%20the%20same%20idea%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20We%20were%20thinking%20late%20last%20year%2C%20independent%20of%20each%20other%2C%20that%20this%20%26quot%3BGriselda%26quot%3B%20thing%20was%20going%20to%20come%20out%20on%20Netflix.%20The%20marketing%20machine%20was%20already%20firing%20up%2C%20and%20it%20was%20apparent%20they%20were%20going%20to%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20juice%20behind%20pushing%20this%20series.%20We%20thought%2C%20what%20can%20we%20do%3F%20We%20knew%20there%20would%20be%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20creative%20license.%20What%20can%20we%20do%20to%20tell%20the%20real%20story%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMichael%2C%20which%20portrayal%20of%20your%20mother%20is%20more%20impressive%3A%20Catherine%20Zeta-Jones'%20in%20%26quot%3BCocaine%20Godmother%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20Sofia%20Vergara's%20in%20%26quot%3BGriselda%26quot%3B%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20would%20love%20to%20be%20able%20to%20comment%20on%20that%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgriselda-blanco-family-settles-lawsuit-against-netflix-sofia-vergara-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebut%20I%20cannot%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20But%2C%20Michael%2C%20you%20really%20liked%20the%20portrayal%20done%20in%20the%20play%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20loved%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zilah%20Mendoza%20in%20a%20white%20fedora%20and%20dress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d53d53f533b039a8858156%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22601%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZilah%20Mendoza%20as%20Griselda%20Blanco%20in%20%26quot%3BConfessions%20of%20a%20Cocaine%20Cowboy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3Erakontur%2FMiami%20New%20Drama%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20remember%20Michael%20holding%20that%20woman%20and%20crying%20outside%20the%20theater%20after%20the%20show.%20Zilah%20Mendoza%20is%20her%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20have%20been%20following%20her%20career%20on%20Instagram.%20I%20have%20sent%20her%20some%20DMs.%20She's%20a%20hell%20of%20an%20actress.%20She%20came%20very%20close%20to%20my%20mother's%20state%20of%20being%20in%20general.%20My%20mother%20was%20a%20very%20rigid%20lady.%20But%20she%20was%20very%20comical.%20Her%20dark%20humor%20was%20that%20of%20a%20woman%20who%20came%20from%20humble%20beginnings.%20My%20mother%20was%20a%20tough%20cookie%2C%20and%20I%20think%20Zilah%20came%20very%20close%20to%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBilly%2C%20is%20there%20a%20highlight%20from%20the%20podcast%20for%20you%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20have%20a%20funny%20exchange%20that%20didn't%20fully%20end%20up%20in%20an%20episode.%20We%20talk%20about%20how%20Sofia%20Vergara%20lights%20a%20huge%20pile%20of%20cocaine%20on%20fire%20that's%20stacked%20in%20an%20empty%20pool.%20I%20couldn't%20even%20zoom%20in%20and%20count%20the%20number%20of%20kilos%3B%20that's%20how%20many%20there%20were.%20Hundreds%20if%20not%20thousands%20of%20kilos%2C%20and%20she%20lights%20it%20on%20fire.%20And%20I%20asked%20Michael%20if%20she%20ever%20did%20that%3B%20that's%20like%20lighting%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20on%20fire.%20He%20said%20of%20course%20not.%20The%20Joker%20does%20it%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Dark%20Knight%26quot%3B%20because%20he's%20an%20anarchist%20and%20insane.%20But%20Griselda%20was%20a%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20Griselda%20Blanco%20such%20a%20fascination%20for%20people%3F%20From%20the%20documentaries%2C%20the%20rap%20songs%2C%20the%20TV%20shows%2C%20the%20play%2C%20why%20has%20she%20become%20a%20fixture%20in%20pop%20culture%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorben%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20think%20it%20starts%20with%20pop%20culture%20having%20a%20fascination%20with%20banditos%20and%20people%20we%20see%20as%20the%20villains.%20Ask%20any%20actor%20why%20they%20prefer%20to%20play%20the%20villain%20than%20the%20hero%3B%20they%20are%20just%20more%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20problem%20is%20when%20people%20reduce%20these%20characters%20to%20single%20dimensions.%20And%20that's%20what%20makes%20Griselda%20so%20compelling%20is%20that%20she%20is%20so%20multifaceted.%20She's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20cocaine%20traffickers%20in%20history.%20At%20the%20dawn%20of%20the%20modern%20industry%20she%20was%20a%20mother%2C%20a%20wife%2C%20a%20daughter%2C%20a%20grandmother%2C%20a%20godmother.%20What%20was%20Al%20Capone%3F%20He%20was%20a%20gangster.%20He%20was%20a%20bootlegger.%20There's%20not%20a%20lot%20to%20him.%20She's%20a%20far%20more%20dynamic%20person%20and%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michael%20Corleone%20Blanco%20speaking%20into%20a%20microphone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c251d97a3d27148878110a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Corleone%20Blanco.%3Cp%3Erakontur%2FYouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMichael%2C%20you%20mention%20a%20%26quot%3Bgenerational%20curse%26quot%3B%20multiple%20times%20on%20the%20podcast.%20Your%20namesake%2C%20Michael%20Corleone%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Godfather%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20brother%20who%20is%20meant%20to%20bring%20legitimacy%20to%20the%20Corleone%20family.%20I%20can't%20help%20but%20see%20the%20similarities%20between%20that%20fictional%20character's%20quest%20and%20your%20own.%20Do%20you%20believe%20that%20you%20went%20through%20all%20this%20because%20you%20were%20chosen%20to%20bring%20legitimacy%20to%20the%20Blanco%20name%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlanco%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Thank%20you%20for%20that.%20100%25.%20I%20tell%20my%20two%20older%20boys%20that%20all%20the%20time.%20It's%20a%20common%20friend%20of%20ours%20who%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20you%20have%20to%20remind%20people%20of%20your%20achievements%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I've%20had%20to%20remind%20myself%20of%20my%20achievements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20part%20of%20that%20generational%20curse%20for%20so%20long.%20I%20speak%20about%20this%20in%20my%20book%3B%20as%20a%2045-year-old%20man%2C%20I%20may%20not%20be%20the%20wisest%2C%20but%20I%20have%20lived%20what%20people%20don't%20live%20in%20two%20or%20three%20lifetimes.%20My%20brothers%20and%20mother%20would%20say%20all%20the%20time%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20show%20the%20face%20for%20the%20family.%20You%20have%20to%20make%20this%20shit%20legit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20return%2C%20I%20was%20robbed%20of%20my%20innocence%20since%20I%20was%20a%20child.%20We%20have%20a%20saying%20in%20Colombia%3A%20%26quot%3BInnocence%20lost%2C%20a%20kilo%20for%20a%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20believe%20all%20generational%20curses%20have%20been%20broken%20in%20my%20family's%20bloodline.%20I'm%20the%20first%20Blanco%20to%20bring%20legit%20money%20home%20and%20I'm%20so%20happy%20and%20proud%20of%20that.%20Even%20this%20podcast%20was%20100%25%20legit.%20My%20mother%20always%20told%20me%20if%20you%20do%20something%2C%20you%20do%20it%20big%20or%20you%20keep%20your%20ass%20at%20home%2C%20and%20we%20did%20it%20big%2C%20and%20we%20did%20it%20legit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20interview%20has%20been%20condensed%20and%20edited%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgriselda-blanco-son-michael-corleone-blanco-podcast-book-interview-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708556434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d666b2a3bd891424f9119c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busine