20speaking%20on%20this%20occasion%2C%20not%20as%20members%20of%20this%20or%20that%20nation%2C%20continent%20or%20creed%2C%20but%20as%20human%20beings%2C%20members%20of%20the%20species%20Man%2C%20whose%20continued%20existence%20is%20in%20doubt.%20The%20world%20is%20full%20of%20conflicts%3B%20and%2C%20overshadowing%20all%20minor%20conflicts%2C%20the%20titanic%20struggle%20between%20Communism%20and%20anti-Communism.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20everybody%20who%20is%20politically%20conscious%20has%20strong%20feelings%20about%20one%20or%20more%20of%20these%20issues%3B%20but%20we%20want%20you%2C%20if%20you%20can%2C%20to%20set%20aside%20such%20feelings%20and%20consider%20yourselves%20only%20as%20members%20of%20a%20biological%20species%20which%20has%20had%20a%20remarkable%20history%2C%20and%20whose%20disappearance%20none%20of%20us%20can%20desire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20shall%20try%20to%20say%20no%20single%20word%20which%20should%20appeal%20to%20one%20group%20rather%20than%20to%20another.%20All%2C%20equally%2C%20are%20in%20peril%2C%20and%2C%20if%20the%20peril%20is%20understood%2C%20there%20is%20hope%20that%20they%20may%20collectively%20avert%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20to%20learn%20to%20think%20in%20a%20new%20way.%20We%20have%20to%20learn%20to%20ask%20ourselves%2C%20not%20what%20steps%20can%20be%20taken%20to%20give%20military%20victory%20to%20whatever%20group%20we%20prefer%2C%20for%20there%20no%20longer%20are%20such%20steps%3B%20the%20question%20we%20have%20to%20ask%20ourselves%20is%3A%20what%20steps%20can%20be%20taken%20to%20prevent%20a%20military%20contest%20of%20which%20the%20issue%20must%20be%20disastrous%20to%20all%20parties%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20public%2C%20and%20even%20many%20men%20in%20positions%20of%20authority%2C%20have%20not%20realized%20what%20would%20be%20involved%20in%20a%20war%20with%20nuclear%20bombs.%20The%20general%20public%20still%20thinks%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20obliteration%20of%20cities.%20It%20is%20understood%20that%20the%20new%20bombs%20are%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20old%2C%20and%20that%2C%20while%20one%20A-bomb%20could%20obliterate%20Hiroshima%2C%20one%20H-bomb%20could%20obliterate%20the%20largest%20cities%2C%20such%20as%20London%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20doubt%20in%20an%20H-bomb%20war%20great%20cities%20would%20be%20obliterated.%20But%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20minor%20disasters%20that%20would%20have%20to%20be%20faced.%20If%20everybody%20in%20London%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20Moscow%20were%20exterminated%20the%20world%20might%2C%20in%20the%20course%20of%20a%20few%20centuries%2C%20recover%20from%20the%20blow.%20But%20we%20now%20know%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20Bikini%20test%2C%20that%20nuclear%20bombs%20can%20gradually%20spread%20destruction%20over%20a%20very%20much%20wider%20area%20than%20had%20been%20supposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20stated%20on%20very%20good%20authority%20that%20a%20bomb%20can%20now%20be%20manufactured%20which%20will%20be%202%2C500%20times%20as%20powerful%20as%20that%20which%20destroyed%20Hiroshima.%20Such%20a%20bomb%2C%20if%20exploded%20near%20the%20ground%20or%20under%20water%2C%20sends%20radio-active%20particles%20into%20the%20upper%20air.%20They%20sink%20gradually%20and%20reach%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20earth%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20deadly%20dust%20or%20rain.%20It%20was%20this%20dust%20which%20infected%20the%20Japanese%20fishermen%20and%20their%20catch%20of%20fish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20knows%20how%20widely%20such%20lethal%20radio-active%20particles%20might%20be%20diffused%2C%20but%20the%20best%20authorities%20are%20unanimous%20in%20saying%20that%20a%20war%20with%20H-bombs%20might%20quite%20possibly%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20human%20race.%20It%20is%20feared%20that%20if%20many%20H-bombs%20are%20used%20there%20will%20be%20universal%20death%20%E2%80%93%20sudden%20only%20for%20a%20minority%2C%20but%20for%20the%20majority%20a%20slow%20torture%20of%20disease%20and%20disintegration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20warnings%20have%20been%20uttered%20by%20eminent%20men%20of%20science%20and%20by%20authorities%20in%20military%20strategy.%20None%20of%20them%20will%20say%20that%20the%20worst%20results%20are%20certain.%20What%20they%20do%20say%2C%20is%20that%20these%20results%20are%20possible%2C%20and%20no%20one%20can%20be%20sure%20that%20they%20will%20not%20be%20realized.%20We%20have%20not%20yet%20found%20that%20the%20views%20of%20experts%20on%20this%20question%20depend%20in%20any%20degree%20upon%20their%20politics%20or%20prejudices.%20They%20depend%20only%2C%20so%20far%20as%20our%20researches%20have%20revealed%2C%20upon%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20particular%20expert%E2%80%99s%20knowledge.%20We%20have%20found%20that%20the%20men%20who%20know%20most%20are%20the%20most%20gloomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20then%2C%20is%20the%20problem%20which%20we%20present%20to%20you%2C%20stark%20and%20dreadful%2C%20and%20inescapable%3A%20Shall%20we%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20human%20race%3A%20or%20shall%20mankind%20renounce%20war%3F1%20People%20will%20not%20face%20this%20alternative%20because%20it%20is%20so%20difficult%20to%20abolish%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20abolition%20of%20war%20will%20demand%20distasteful%20limitations%20of%20national%20sovereignty.2%20But%20what%20perhaps%20impedes%20understanding%20of%20the%20situation%20more%20than%20anything%20else%20is%20that%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Cmankind%E2%80%9D%20feels%20vague%20and%20abstract.%20People%20scarcely%20realize%20in%20imagination%20that%20the%20danger%20is%20to%20themselves%20and%20their%20children%20and%20their%20grandchildren%2C%20and%20not%20only%20to%20a%20dimly%20apprehended%20humanity.%20They%20can%20scarcely%20bring%20themselves%20to%20grasp%20that%20they%2C%20individually%2C%20and%20those%20whom%20they%20love%20are%20in%20imminent%20danger%20of%20perishing%20agonizingly.%20And%20so%20they%20hope%20that%20perhaps%20war%20may%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue%20provided%20modern%20weapons%20are%20prohibited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20hope%20is%20illusory.%20Whatever%20agreements%20not%20to%20use%20H-bombs%20had%20been%20reached%20in%20time%20of%20peace%2C%20they%20would%20no%20longer%20be%20considered%20binding%20in%20time%20of%20war%2C%20and%20both%20sides%20would%20set%20to%20work%20to%20manufacture%20H-bombs%20as%20soon%20as%20war%20broke%20out%2C%20for%2C%20if%20one%20side%20manufactured%20the%20bombs%20and%20the%20other%20did%20not%2C%20the%20side%20that%20manufactured%20them%20would%20inevitably%20be%20victorious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20an%20agreement%20to%20renounce%20nuclear%20weapons%20as%20part%20of%20a%20general%20reduction%20of%20armaments3%20would%20not%20afford%20an%20ultimate%20solution%2C%20it%20would%20serve%20certain%20important%20purposes.%20First%3A%20any%20agreement%20between%20East%20and%20West%20is%20to%20the%20good%20in%20so%20far%20as%20it%20tends%20to%20diminish%20tension.%20Second%3A%20the%20abolition%20of%20thermo-nuclear%20weapons%2C%20if%20each%20side%20believed%20that%20the%20other%20had%20carried%20it%20out%20sincerely%2C%20would%20lessen%20the%20fear%20of%20a%20sudden%20attack%20in%20the%20style%20of%20Pearl%20Harbour%2C%20which%20at%20present%20keeps%20both%20sides%20in%20a%20state%20of%20nervous%20apprehension.%20We%20should%20therefore%20welcome%20such%20an%20agreement%2C%20though%20only%20as%20a%20first%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20us%20are%20not%20neutral%20in%20feeling%2C%20but%2C%20as%20human%20beings%2C%20we%20have%20to%20remember%20that%2C%20if%20the%20issues%20between%20East%20and%20West%20are%20to%20be%20decided%20in%20any%20manner%20that%20can%20give%20any%20possible%20satisfaction%20to%20anybody%2C%20whether%20Communist%20or%20anti-Communist%2C%20whether%20Asian%20or%20European%20or%20American%2C%20whether%20White%20or%20Black%2C%20then%20these%20issues%20must%20not%20be%20decided%20by%20war.%20We%20should%20wish%20this%20to%20be%20understood%20both%20in%20the%20East%20and%20in%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20lies%20before%20us%2C%20