ry%20of%20luxury%20haircare.%20You've%20guessed%20it%3A%20our%20pick%20for%20the%20best%20overall%20diffuser%20for%20curly%20hair%20is%20The%20Dyson%20Supersonic%20Hair%20Dryer%2C%20which%20comes%20with%20a%20coveted%20diffuser%20attachment.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20the%20way%20Dyson%20diffuses%20the%20heat%2C%20which%20is%20healthier%20for%20the%20hair%20while%20enhancing%20the%20shape%20of%20the%20curls%20beautifully%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Christophe%20Robin%2C%20hair%20salon%20owner%20and%20luxury%20haircare%20line%20founder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Dyson%20Supersonic%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20pricey%20hair%20dryers%20on%20the%20list%2C%20it%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-hair-dryer%5C%22%3Ebest%20hair%20dryer%3C%2Fa%3E%20we've%20ever%20tried.%20What%20makes%20it%20worth%20it%20for%20curly%20hair%20is%20not%20just%20the%20diffuser%20but%20how%20the%20dryer%20works%20with%20the%20diffuser%20to%20get%20you%20perfect%20curls.%20It%20contains%20negative%20ions%20that%20help%20diminish%20static%2C%20which%20helps%20prevent%20frizz.%20Plus%20Dyson's%20intelligent%20heat%20control%20technology%20helps%20to%20prevent%20heat%20damage%2C%20which%20is%20especially%20important%20for%20those%20with%20fragile%20curls.%20According%20to%20New%20York%20City%20hair%20colorist%20and%20Founder%20of%20Abby%20Haliti%20Color%20Studio%20Abby%20Halit%2C%20the%20dryer%20%26quot%3Bgets%20the%20job%20done%20quickly%2C%20but%20still%20keeps%20the%20definition%20and%20shape%20of%20the%20curls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20quick%20dry%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20faster%20you%20dry%20your%20hair%2C%20the%20more%20moisture%20it%20will%20lose%2C%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20moisture%20is%20not%20good%20for%20maintaining%20the%20curl%20pattern%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Christophe%20Robin.%20The%20reason%20for%20this%20is%20that%20drying%20your%20hair%20often%20requires%20high%20heat%2C%20and%20elevated%20temperatures%20can%20weaken%20curly%20strands%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20a%20brittle%2C%20dehydrated%20texture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20take%20your%20time%20while%20diffusing.%20However%2C%20many%20of%20us%20have%20busy%20schedules%2C%20so%20time%20isn't%20always%20on%20our%20side.%20In%20the%20event%20that%20you're%20in%20desperate%20need%20of%20a%20quick%20dry%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20compromise%20the%20health%20of%20your%20curls%2C%20The%20DevaDiffuser%20by%20Deva%20Curl%20will%20do%20the%20trick.%20DevaCurl's%20hand-shaped%20diffuser%20is%20one%20of%20a%20kind%E2%80%94%20it's%20literally%20patented%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20structure%20is%20designed%20to%20target%20the%20roots%2C%20helping%20to%20dry%20curls%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20travel%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20constantly%20on%20the%20go%20but%20want%20to%20keep%20your%20curls%20fresh%20during%20travel%2C%20you'll%20need%20a%20small%20tool%20with%20a%20diffuser%20that%20you%20can%20easily%20store%20in%20your%20suitcase.%20If%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20buy%20a%20separate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-travel-hair-dryers%5C%22%3Etravel%20hair%20dryer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20then%20fuss%20with%20buying%20a%20diffuser%20that%20fits%2C%20this%20is%20the%20perfect%20tool%20since%20it%20comes%20all%20in%20one.%20Revlon's%201875W%20Natural%20Texture%20Diffuser%20Hair%20Dryer%20is%20probably%20the%20cutest%20hair%20dryer%20you'll%20ever%20see%2C%20plus%20it's%20only%20%2435.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20traveling%2C%20the%20last%20thing%20you%20want%20to%20do%20is%20spend%20endless%20time%20in%20your%20hotel%20bathroom%20styling%20your%20hair%2C%20so%20this%20tool%20definitely%20comes%20in%20handy%20as%20it%20allows%20you%20to%20dry%20your%20hair%20quickly%20and%20effectively.%20Designed%20with%201875%20watts%2C%20Revlon's%20diffuser%20has%20a%20super%20strong%20airflow%2C%20and%20the%20mou