0of%20natural%20dimension.%20But%20there's%20no%20harm%20in%20enhancing%20what's%20already%20there!%20Thanks%20to%20Segbeauty's%20Hair%20Diffuser%2C%20creating%20a%20voluminous%20look%20is%20easier%20than%20ever.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Segbeauty%20Hair%20Diffuser%20is%20great%20for%20volume%20because%20it%20distributes%20heat%20evenly%20and%20has%20a%20larger%20bowl%20for%20hair%20to%20sit%20in%2C%20which%20also%20helps%20cut%20down%20on%20drying%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20hairstylist%20Cassandra%20Olivia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20dispersing%20steady%20airflow%2C%20large%20diffuser%20bowls%20are%20also%20great%20for%20drying%20and%20defining%20long%20hair.%20Those%20with%20lengthy%20curls%20know%20that%20diffusing%20can%20be%20a%20hassle%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20dealing%20with%20an%20attachment%20with%20a%20shallow%20bowl%20with%20short%20prongs.%20Diffusers%20designed%20in%20this%20way%20often%20cause%20hair%20strands%20to%20spill%20over%20the%20bowl's%20sides%2C%20leading%20to%20uneven%20drying%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20curl%20definition.%20So%2C%20if%20you're%20someone%20with%20long%20hair%20who%20is%20looking%20to%20enhance%20the%20volume%20of%20your%20stands%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20add%20this%20product%20to%20your%20shopping%20cart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20eliminating%20frizz%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20spiral-like%20shape%20of%20curls%2C%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20for%20natural%20oils%20to%20spread%20from%20your%20scalp%20throughout%20your%20hair%20strands%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20moisture%20and%20increased%20dryness.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20frizz%20is%20inevitable%2C%20but%20there%20are%20certainly%20ways%20to%20manage%20wispy%20strands.%20Hair%20stylist%20Cassandra%20Olivia%20notes%20that%20the%20first%20step%20is%20to%20apply%20a%20leave-in%20product%20before%20diffusing%20curls%20to%20help%20enhance%20their%20shape%20as%20they%20dry%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20apply%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C