d%20wind.%20For%20those%20struggling%20with%20damaged%20hair%20or%20sensitive%20scalps%2C%20or%20if%20you%20simply%20want%20a%20healthy%20alternative%20to%20beauty%20tools%20that%20use%20aggressive%20heat%2C%20we'd%20recommend%20using%20this%20diffuser%20to%20protect%20and%20rejuvenate%20your%20curls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3Cp%3EInvesting%20in%20a%20diffuser%20is%20important%20for%20curly%20hair%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20have%20to%20go%20out%20and%20buy%20an%20entirely%20new%20beauty%20tool.%20If%20you%20already%20own%20a%20hair%20dryer%2C%20all%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20purchase%20a%20diffuser%20attachment%20that%20aligns%20with%20the%20size%20of%20your%20dryer.%20Conair's%20Volumizing%20Hair%20Diffuser%20is%20sold%20between%20%2410%20and%20%2413%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20retailer%2C%20and%20can%20fit%20any%20hair%20dryer%20between%201.8%20to%202.3%20inches.%20In%20addition%20to%20not%20breaking%20the%20bank%2C%20this%20diffuser%20is%20substantial%20concerning%20quality.%20The%20prongs%20attached%20to%20Conair's%20Diffuser%20are%20designed%20to%20lift%20and%20dry%20hair%20gently%20to%20mold%20perfectly%20defined%20curls.%20Reviewers%20also%20love%20that%20the%20diffuser%20attachment%20cups%20each%20curl%20nicely%20while%20enhancing%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20if%20your%20hair%20dryer%20is%20incompatible%20with%20the%20Conair%20Volumizing%20Hair%20Diffuser%20(i.e.%20if%20it's%20less%20than%201.8%20inches%20or%20more%20than%202.3%20inches)%2C%20plenty%20of%20diffuser%20attachments%20come%20in%20various%20sizes%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20tight%20curls%3Cp%3ECurly%20hair%20is%20not%20one-dimensional%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20types%2C%20patterns%2C%20and%20textures%20that%20exist.%20This%20means%20that%20not%20every%20product%20or%20tool%20will%20work%20universally%20across%20curly%20hair%2C%20and%20as%20someone%20with%20tight%20curls%2C%20finding%20the%20right%20products%20for%20my%20coils%20can%20be%20difficult.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETight%20curls%20are%20typically%20more%20dense%20and%20difficult%20to%20dry%2C%20so%20using%20a%20diffuser%20tool%20that%20has%20sufficient%20airflow%20that%20spreads%20evenly%20across%20hair%20strands%20is%20essential.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20the%20CONFU%20Professional%20Hair%20Dryer%20with%20Diffuser%20for%20curly%20and%20coily%20hair%2C%26quot%3B%20Cassandra%20Olivia%20tells%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20diffuser%20has%20extra-long%20prongs%2C%20so%20it%20can%20get%20into%20thicker%20hair%20right%20to%20the%20scalp%20to%20ensure%20I%20am%20evenly%20and%20effectively%20drying%20hair.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EExperts%20we%20consulted%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbby%20Halit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20hair%20colorist%2C%20world-renowned%20master%20of%20the%20contemporary%20European%20technique%20of%20French%20Balayage%2C%20and%20Founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abbyhaliti.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAbby%20Haliti%20Color%20Studio%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECassandra%20Olivia%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_cassandraolivia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehair%20stylist%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20licensed%20cosmetologist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChristophe%20Robin%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20world-leading%20colorist%2C%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.christopherobin.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristophe%20Robin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20owner%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.christophe-robin.salon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristophe%20Robin%20Salon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fb