pients%20of%20EU%20Sanctions%20For%20Alleged%20Aid%20to%20Russia%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22010858%2F30917373084_c169edccc3_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20An%20Indian%20company%20is%20among%20the%20targets%20of%20a%20fresh%20sanctions%20package%20agreed%20upon%20by%20the%20European%20Union%20(EU)%20that%20is%20directed%20at%20entities%20accused%20of%20supporting%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20war%20against%20Ukraine%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F7ef97342-48fa-4969-b3ee-bc7419b69e65%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20200%20entities%20and%20individuals%20in%20total%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20latest%20sanctions%20either%20for%20their%20alleged%20role%20in%20helping%20Russia%20procure%20weapons%20or%20of%20involvement%20in%20kidnapping%20Ukrainian%20children%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feu-approves-13th-sanctions-package-against-russia-eu-sources-2024-02-21%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20report%20by%20Reuters%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20company%20is%20accused%20of%20helping%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98war%20machine%E2%80%99%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-21%2Feu-approves-more-russia-sanctions-following-navalny-s-death%3Fsrnd%3Dpremium-europe%5C%22%3Eaccess%20banned%20components%20and%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Bloomberg%20news%20agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sanctions%20proposal%20was%20cited%20by%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20also%20appropriate%20to%20include%20on%20that%20list%20certain%20other%20entities%20in%20third%20countries%20that%20indirectly%20support%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20military%20and%20industrial%20complex%E2%80%89%E2%80%A6%E2%80%89by%20trading%20in%20such%20components.%E2