from%20the%20members%E2%80%99%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20IDU%20to%20inquire%20about%20the%20current%20membership%20status%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%2C%20if%20not%20a%20member%2C%20the%20rationale%20behind%20their%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20emailed%20reply%2C%20the%20secretary%20general%20of%20IDU%2C%20Tina%20Mercep%2C%20replied%20that%20the%20IDU%20%E2%80%9Cenjoys%20a%20warm%20and%20open%20dialogue%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20would%20welcome%20full%20membership%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20our%20global%20network%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMercep%2C%20a%20Croatian%20politician%2C%20also%20wrote%20that%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20youth%20organisation%20remains%20a%20member%20of%20the%20youth%20wing%20of%20the%20IDU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20IDU%2C%20the%20member%20political%20parties%20profess%20the%20%E2%80%9Cideals%20of%20liberal%20democracy%2C%20freedom%20of%20the%20individual%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20economic%20growth%20to%20be%20based%20on%20individual%20initiative%20and%20free%2C%20competitive%20enterprise%20economies%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20it%20says%20that%20through%20the%20IDU%2C%20the%20members%20could%20%E2%80%9Cexchange%20policy%20ideas%2C%20assist%20each%20other%20to%20win%20the%20political%20argument%2C%20and%20to%20win%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708514066000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30161148%2F406110211_773446158163006_4756603232278021214_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-conspicuous-by-absence-from-global-centre-right-political-parties-alliance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20BJP%20has%20not%20been%20among%20the%20members%20of%20International%20Democracy%20Union%20for%20at%20least%20six%20months%20now%2C%20the%20Munich-based%20organisation%20has%20said%20it%20is%20happy%20to%20welcome%20BJP%20return%20to%20'full%20membership'.%22%