-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20appealed%20to%20the%20community%20to%20adopt%20malnourished%20kids%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20proper%20nutritional%20care.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20community%2C%20by%20the%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20Integrated%20Management%20of%20Acute%20Malnutrition%20(IMAM)%20programme%20of%20the%20Indian%20Government%2C%20which%20provides%20take-home%20rations%20to%20children%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20appealed%20to%20the%20community%20of%20Katni%20to%20adopt%20malnourished%20kids%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20proper%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F114640%2Futtar-pradesh-malnutrition-breast-feeding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enutritional%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20this%20programme%2C%20anyone%20can%20volunteer%20to%20look%20after%20malnourished%20children.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20nutrition%20kits%20for%20at%20least%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%20The%20kits%20comprise%20a%20variety%20of%20vitamin%20and%20protein-rich%20food%20products%20%E2%80%94%20including%20amla%20candy%2C%20soybean%20nuggets%2C%20grams%2C%20%3Cem%3Esattu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Horlicks%2C%20jaggery%2C%20groundnuts%2C%20and%20lentils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20District%20Collector%20roped%20in%20a%20team%20of%20paediatricians%2C%20child%20nutritionists%2C%20and%20experts%20from%20the%20women%20and%20child%20development%20department%20to%20come%20up%20with%20the%20kit%2C%20specially%20designed%20for%20malnourished%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20providing%20rations%20worth%20Rs%20600%20per%20child%20every%20month.%20This%20ration%20kit%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20provided%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20month.%20The%20additional%20ration%20support%20was%20given