ending%20case%2C%20Laxmi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20married%20off%20our%20daughter%20and%20have%20also%20been%20bearing%20medical%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20a%20month.%20To%20manage%20these%20expenses%2C%20we%20took%20loans%20worth%20Rs%205%20lakh.%20To%20repay%20the%20loan%20amounts%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20sell%20the%20land.%20So%20we%20brought%20our%20case%20to%20the%20collectorate%E2%80%99s%20notice%20but%20nobody%20listened%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20January%2C%20her%20case%20was%20resolved.%20%E2%80%9CThanks%20to%20the%20present%20DM%20%3Cem%3Esahab%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eour%20case%20got%20finalised%20in%20the%20second%20hearing%2C%20and%20we%20got%20the%20permission%20to%20sell%20our%20land.%20There%20were%20people%20in%20our%20village%20whose%20cases%20were%20pending%20for%20as%20long%20as%20five%20years%3B%20their%20cases%20were%20resolved%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20farmer%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Basti%20district%E2%80%99s%20Palha%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FBasti-1708349565.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Last%20September%2C%20IAS%20Vamsi%20Andra%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20District%20Collector%20of%20the%20Basti%20district.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FBasti-1708349565.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FBasti-1708349565-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FBasti-1708349565-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FBasti-1708349565-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FBasti-1708349565-150x7