urthermore%2C%20millets%20grow%20in%20low-fertility%20soils%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20need%20too%20much%20water.%20They%20just%20need%20timely%20rain%20to%20get%20a%20good%20harvest%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Saju%20Parackal%2C%20CEO%2C%20Dream%20India%20Network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20tech%20to%20revive%20traditions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo3-1708067458-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IHRD%20College%20students%20volunteer%20alongside%20Lenovo%20volunteers%20oversee%20the%20Tech%20Centre.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo3-1708067458-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo3-1708067458-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo3-1708067458-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo3-1708067458-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo3-1708067458-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo3-1708067458-2048x1152.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo3-1708067458-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342037%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIHRD%20College%20students%20volunteer%20alongside%20Lenovo%20volunteers%20to%20oversee%20the%20tech%20centre.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELenovo%20then%20got%20on%20to%20set%20up%20the%20%E2%80%98Lenovo%20Digital%20Centre%20for%20Kanthalloor%20Millets%E2%80%99%20at%20IHRD%